    content={'During one sprint, I collaborated on a forked version of the open-source app <a href="https://solara-next-task.netlify.app/" target="_blank" class="text-link underline">NextTask</a>. A teammate handled the development, while I focused on writing a detailed ##test plan## covering several key ##features## and ##user stories##.'}
