    content={"I used ##Xray## and ##Jira## to manage test cases and bug reports, with full documentation structured in ##Confluence##. The testing focused on core CRUD operations and ensuring traceability from requirements to test coverage."}
  />
  <Paragraph
    content={"You can view the original app on the previous link and check the test documentation on the button below."}
  />
  <div class="modal-buttons !justify-end">
    <a
      href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1PvnlGZutKLkBdqrxGEgLMc1Hs_BZF9Js?usp=sharing"
      target="_blank"
